title: How To Integrate Your Hamilton Hills Smart Lighting with Google Assistant
description:
This video explains how to integrate your Hamilton Hills App with Google. After integrating you will be able to use Google to control your Hamilton Hills Smart lighting. 

For Example say “Hey Google turn off all lights"

Link to Hamilton Hills App on the Apple App Store:
https://apps.apple.com/us/app/hamilton-hills-smart/id1459996652

Link to Hamilton Hills App on the Google Play Store:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.bright.cn
